, FinTech financial technology, Global business, online banking, interbank payment concept. Man using mobile phone and laptop computer with international currency\" data-id=\"1442930115\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"945px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442930115/image_1442930115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442930115/image_1442930115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442930115/image_1442930115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442930115/image_1442930115.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442930115/image_1442930115.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442930115/image_1442930115.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442930115/image_1442930115.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442930115/image_1442930115.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">International Money Express (IMXI)</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Tippapatt/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares in <strong>International Money Express</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IMXI\" title=\"International Money Express, Inc.\">IMXI</a></span>), better known as <strong>Intermex</strong>, have performed well since I initially wrote about the remittance services company <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723214-international-money-express-this-global-remittance-play-is-now-an-activist-target\">back in September</a>. Over the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442930115/image_1442930115.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745539-international-money-express-key-catalysts-strengthening-as-new-catalysts-emerge", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 15:35:29", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745416", "title": "How Amazon Advanced Its Prime Video Down The Court To Set Up Bigger 2025", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1343564662/image_1343564662.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Large Amazon distribution warehouse\" data-id=\"1343564662\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1031px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1343564662/image_1343564662.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1343564662/image_1343564662.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1343564662/image_1343564662.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1343564662/image_1343564662.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1343564662/image_1343564662.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1343564662/image_1343564662.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1343564662/image_1343564662.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1343564662/image_1343564662.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-cre